{
  "stem": "6277.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- then I was working on [INAUDIBLE], in the same building where I went to school, my same-- the school where I learn.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and there I was working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And heating, it was a very hard-- hard job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were heating three stories, the building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were heating all the ovens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would carry the wood in-- in the ovens, clean out the rooms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very hard job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- so we-- we spent the whole winter there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we went-- we-- in the beginning, we want-- we would go home to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later, it was hard for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to go every day and pick us up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then if they needed something at night or in the evening, they couldn't help us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they need some-- what was something to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So for them, it were more-- more convenient to have us there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they asked the administration of the ghetto to allow them to hold them in the working place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called it [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It means outside installations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we were-- we lived there in the school, where we worked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was many such [GERMAN] in this-- in Riga, then, in that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And about how many people were in the group that you--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--were in?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a small group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were about six people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We slept in the-- the cellar, or in there, where we were taking off our clothes when we went to school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there they gave us a small room, and there we sleep-- slept.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a little better, because you didn't have to go through the search every night.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
